Package ulrichbarnstedt.lib.output.render.elments

Elements for the pseudo-rendering engine.

See: Description

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Container
    List of elements which can either be rendered horizontally or vertically
    Element
    Base class for all renderable elements.
    ElementBox<T extends ElementBox<T>>
    Abstract class representing table-like containers
    Empty
    Empty element, can be used in tables to force columns/rows to have padding applied
    MultilineText
    Text spanning over multiple lines
    Screen
    The base renderer for elements, base for displaying
    ScreenManager
    Automatically manage screens
    Spacer
    Spacing between elements
    SubdividedTable
    Table element with borders around each separate element
    Table
    Table element, without borders around the elements.
    Text
    Single, renderable line of text Note: actually only renders one high, so using line breaks is not an option
